    <div class="single-header__title text-center text-sm-left">
      <h1>Een nieuwe website om de lezers op Europees niveau te informeren</h1>
            <div class="d-bloc my-2 publish_date_time">Gepubliceerd op 26 mei 2020 om 10:25</div>    </div>
    <div class="single-header__author">
      <ul>
                  <li><a href="https://voxeurop.eu/nl/author/redactionve/" title="Berichten van Voxeurop editorial board" class="author url fn" rel="author">Voxeurop editorial board</a>                      </li>
                          <li>Translated by <a
              href="https://voxeurop.eu/nl/author/geertjebureau-virgule-com/">gteunissen</a>
          </li>
                      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="single-article__language single-article__language__mobile">
      <ul> <li><a class='nl wpml-ls-link'  href='javascript:void(0)'>nl </a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link fr" href="https://voxeurop.eu/fr/un-nouveau-site-pour-informer-a-hauteur-deuropeens/">fr</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link en" href="https://voxeurop.eu/en/a-new-website-for-informing-on-a-european-scale/">en</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link cs" href="https://voxeurop.eu/cs/novy-web-na-evropske-urovni/">cs</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link de" href="https://voxeurop.eu/de/eine-neue-website-um-sie-auf-europaeischem-niveau-zu-informieren/">de</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link it" href="https://voxeurop.eu/it/un-nuovo-sito-per-informarsi-ad-altezza-europea/">it</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pt-pt" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pt-pt/um-novo-site-para-informar-a-nivel-europeu/">pt-pt</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link ro" href="https://voxeurop.eu/ro/un-nou-site-de-informare-la-nivelul-europenilor/">ro</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link es" href="https://voxeurop.eu/es/una-nueva-pagina-web-para-informar-a-nivel-europeo/">es</a></li><li><a class="wpml-ls-link pl" href="https://voxeurop.eu/pl/nowa-strona-informujaca-wszystkich-europejczykow/">pl</a></li></ul>      <div class="mobile-language-separator"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="single-header__image">
              <div class="single-header__image__container">
